{"word":"G3726 - ὁρκίζω - horkízō - hor-kid'-zo - Adjure","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁρκίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">horkízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hor-kid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Adjure</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆணையிடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to force to take an oath, to administer an oath to"},{"paragraph":"2. to adjure"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3727 - ὅρκος - hórkos - hor'-kos/3727\">G3727</a>; to <i>put on oath</i>, that is, <i>make swear</i>; by analogy to solemnly <i>enjoin:</i> - adjure, charge.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1844/1844\">G1844</a>, <a href=\"#/G1845/1845\">G1845</a>, <a href=\"#/G1964/1964\">G1964</a>, <a href=\"#/G1965/1965\">G1965</a>, <a href=\"#/G3726/3726\">G3726</a>, <a href=\"#/G3727/3727\">G3727</a>, <a href=\"#/G3728/3728\">G3728</a>"}]}